<subSubSection pageId="267" pageNumber="268" type="note">
<paragraph pageId="267" pageNumber="268">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="267" pageNumber="268">This species, also known under the vernacular name &quot;Delta Green Ground Beetle&quot;, is considered an endangered species by the World Wildlife Fund and listed on the IUCN Red List of Threatened Species.</paragraph>
